headline: Procare Solutions Launches Accredited Professional Development Training for Child Care Providers
summary: Procare Solutions, a leader in child care management software, is pleased to announce the launch of Procare Professional Development to encourage and support busy early childhood education providers in maintaining training compliance while elevating the quality of education that young learners receive.
